      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 22,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kaedehara Kazuha_icon.png",
                      "name": "楓原萬葉",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "楓原萬葉的固有天賦「風物之詩詠」能夠以自身",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "為基礎轉化為全隊的對應",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素傷害加成",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "。此武器副詞條能為楓原萬葉提供較高的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "，可以有效提升楓原萬葉固有天賦的增益效果。作為活動贈送的武器，對精通增傷流的楓原萬葉來說是不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2256,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kuki Shinobu_icon.png",
                      "name": "久岐忍",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "固有天賦「安心之所」能夠基於自身的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "，提高自身",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素戰技",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "的治療量和傷害值。該武器副詞條能為久岐忍提供較高的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "，可以有效提升久岐忍固有天賦的增益效果。作為活動贈送的武器，對於精通流久岐忍來說是不錯的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
